Hello everybody! I am really sorry that I haven't written in a long time but guess what I got a call last week on thursday that my liver was in and I had to come into the hospital. The next day I got my liver transplant. The liver came from a 17 year old girl. That really made me sad to hear that but that girl saved my life and the life of a baby. I got part of the liver(the biggest) and a baby at Childrens Hospital got another part of the liver.
 Well I guess this is a good way to start off the New Year lol. Anyway I just want to let you all know I am still at the hospital and I am doing just fine. I am a little sore and extremley exhausted but thats ok. My scar is pretty cool it almost looks like a Mercedes Benz symbol lol. I am in my hospital room and i have access to the internet in my room so goody! 

I also heard that you people got the day off from school today YEAHHHH! That a day off for you and one less day to make up for me :)

Well I just wanted to let everyone know so they wouldn't worry and i miss u all like crazy and i can't wait to see you all again.   

                                                 Love ~*Nichole*~
